VALUES
		("en_US", 
		"LOC_BUILDING_UNIVERSITY_SANKORE_DESCRIPTION",					
		"International [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Routes sent from this city provide +1 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and +1 [ICON_FAITH] Faith for every two followers of the city's majority Religion. [NEWLINE]+2 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science and +1 [ICON_FAITH] Faith for every [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Route to this city. Other civilization's [ICON_TRADEROUTE] Trade Routes provide +2 [ICON_SCIENCE] Science for them.[NEWLINE][ICON_TRADEROUTE]Trade Routes from your Civilization exert +7 [ICON_LEU_RELIGIOUS_PRESSURE] Religious Pressure to the Destination city, and receive +3 [ICON_LEU_RELIGIOUS_PRESSURE] Religious Pressure from it.[NEWLINE]Must be built on a Desert or Desert Hills tile next to a Campus with a University.");
